{
  "stem": "10829.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was also in charge of the-- of the-- of the forest surrounding-- surrounding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When the policeman used to come in, I remember, they used to come in town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They used to stop [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Part of the reason we had a-- had the city store, we had everything around there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then he used to-- we had fields, and he used to take care of that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the biggest part that I remember of-- of my dad is being all over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as a little kid, he used to take me around, the all-- the second kid in the family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And a boy, he always used to carry me around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And wherever he went, I used to go-- go with my dad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But at this time-- and a lot of times I get scared-- I remember my dad's features, but I don't remember his face.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I can describe to you what he-- what he's tall and everything else, but his face is fading away at this time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But our town-- let me-- going back a little bit, talking about our town and the life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The life in Trochenbrod was very simple.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were surrounded by Ukraines and Poles, as I said before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The villagers and European lifestyle was very rough or dangerous, at least in our shtetl.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But dangerous when it came-- when it came holidays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "For instance, even now, Pesach-- I'll give you an example-- where everybody used to sit, and we'd sing and all this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We used to close our shutters, close all this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "One of the worst times that we had around Pesach, when you open up the door for [NON-ENGLISH], that's when everybody used to be scared.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because the Polacks around those time, and the Ukrainians, they used to attack the-- the-- the-- village.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The city.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
